Flight						KEY:Dracha ~ Flight								CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Extraordinary.Dracha Race Trait.Race Ability.SpecialQuality	DESC:Dracha with two racial levels can use their wings to fly, taking their ground speed as their flight speed. The dracha can even wear medium or heavy armor while flying. They have clumsy maneuverability, which improves to average at 3rd level. (See page 177 for more on flying maneuverability.)
