Evolved Dracha Breath Weapon			KEY:Dracha ~ Evolved Dracha Breath Weapon					CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Dracha Race Trait.Race Ability.SpecialQuality	DESC:This is a cone of fire, cold, acid, or electricity (character choice, but once made it cannot be changed) 30 feet long that inflicts 1d6 points of damage per character level (maximum 2d6 per dracha racial or evolved level). Reflex save (DC 10 + dracha levels + Constitution modifier) halves damage. Usable once per day for every two dracha racial or evolved levels. This standard action does not provoke an attack of opportunity.
Evolved Dracha Natural Armor Bonus		KEY:Dracha ~ Evolved Dracha Natural Armor Bonus				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Extraordinary.Dracha Race Trait.Race Ability.SpecialQuality	DESC:These bonuses stack with the dracha’s existing natural armor bonus.
Evolved Dracha Claws				KEY:Dracha ~ Evolved Dracha Claws						CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Extraordinary.Dracha Race Trait.Race Ability.SpecialQuality	DESC:Dracha claws on both hands become usable natural weapons at 5th level, inflicting 1d8 points of damage. The dracha can make off-hand attacks if he wishes (using the normal penalties). As with any melee weapon, the dracha adds his Strength bonus to attack and damage rolls made with the claws (use half Strength bonus for damage bonuses to off-hand attacks).
Evolved Dracha Flight				KEY:Dracha ~ Evolved Dracha Flight						CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Extraordinary.Dracha Race Trait.Race Ability.SpecialQuality	DESC:Dracha flight maneuverability increases to good at 5th level and perfect at 6th level.
Evolved Dracha Pounce				KEY:Dracha ~ Evolved Dracha Pounce						CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Extraordinary.Dracha Race Trait.Race Ability.SpecialQuality	DESC:The 6th-level evolved dracha can attempt a charge attack if flying and still make a special full attack with his bite and claws, or his bite, one claw, and one weapon (making only one attack with the weapon even though he normally would have iterative attacks due to his high base attack bonus).

