Distinct Voice			KEY:Magister ~ Distinct Voice				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:MagisterLesserAspectofPower.SpecialQuality.Supernatural											DESC:Whenever you wish, anyone within 100 feet can hear you, regardless of noise around you, even when whispering.
